<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd" identifier="medication-dose-weight" title="Dosis de medicamento y peso máximo del paciente" adaptive="false" time-dependent="false">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>La dosis de un medicamento solo es efectiva si se suministran como mínimo 25 mg por kilogramo una vez al día, pero la dosis diaria no puede ser mayor que 2000 mg.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuántos kilogramos, como máximo, debe tener un paciente para que este medicamento sea efectivo y no supere la dosis diaria?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">25 kg</qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">55 kg</qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">80 kg</qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">105 kg</qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing template="https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml"/>
</qti-assessment-item>